title: Order relative to authorizing the joint committee on Community Development and Small Businesses to make an investigation and study of a certain current Senate documents relative to community development

abstracts.abstract: Senate, November 6, 2025 -- The committee on Community Development and Small Businesses, to whom was referred the petitions (accompanied by bill, Senate, No. 182) of Vincent Dixon, for legislation for community housing packages, report the accompanying Order  (Senate, No. 2699).
